Nadia Ali (broadcaster) https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Nadia_Ali_(broadcaster) 0 Nadia Ali (Bengali: নদিয়া আলী; born 15 November 1984) is an English television and radio presenter of Bangladeshi descent. She is best known for presenting the Sunday evening show on BBC Asian Network.
